overview: DEMANSOL is one of the biggest Games and Applications Development Firms in India specializing in entertainment applications for iPhone and Android platforms. More than 200 of Demansol’s creations are in the App Store now, many of which have been featured in the Top 100 in their categories. Demansol continues to expand, fulfilling their goal of providing users with the greatest games and apps for their mobile phones. Our team continues to grow and replenish with talented game developers, programmers, sound makers, and with creative people who are willing to relieve the monotony of iPhone games/applications area.
